 <!-- All life paths -->
 <section id="all-life-paths" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
 <h2 class="section-h2">All life path numbers at a glance</h2>

 <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed mb-6">
 Life paths run 1 to 9, plus three master numbers that don't reduce. Each carries its own energy. Seeing the 2 in relation to 1, 3, or 7 shows you how they interact and which pairings work.
 </p>

 <div class="lp-grid">
 {[
 { n: 1, label: "The Leader", href: "/learn/life-path-number-1/" },
 { n: 2, label: "The Peacemaker", href: "/learn/life-path-number-2/", active: true },
