 <!-- How to calculate -->
 <section id="calculate" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
 <h2 class="section-h2">How to find your life path number</h2>

 <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed mb-4">
 Your life path number is derived from your birth date. Reduce the day, month, and year each to a single digit, then add those three digits together and reduce again. If any stage produces 11, 22, or 33, don't reduce further - those are master numbers.
 </p>

 <div class="card-light" style="padding:1.25rem 1.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;">
 <div style="font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-body-text);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Example: November 20, 1991</div>
 <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.4rem;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--color-muted-text);">
 <div style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;"><span style="color:var(--color-violet);font-weight:600;width:4rem;">Month:</span> November = <strong style="color:var(--color-body-text);margin-left:0.25rem;">11 → keep as 11 (master number)</strong></div>
 <div style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;"><span style="color:var(--color-violet);font-weight:600;width:4rem;">Day:</span> 20 → 2+0 = <strong style="color:var(--color-body-text);margin-left:0.25rem;">2</strong></div>
 <div style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;"><span style="color:var(--color-violet);font-weight:600;width:4rem;">Year:</span> 1991 → 1+9+9+1 = 20 → 2+0 = <strong style="color:var(--color-body-text);margin-left:0.25rem;">2</strong></div>
 <div style="border-top:1px solid var(--color-border);padding-top:0.4rem;display:flex;gap:0.5rem;"><span style="color:var(--color-violet);font-weight:600;width:4rem;">Total:</span> 11+2+2 = 15 → 1+5 = <strong style="color:var(--color-soft-gold);font-size:1rem;margin-left:0.25rem;">6</strong></div>
 </div>
 </div>

 <p class="text-body-text leading-relaxed mb-4">
 Use your own birth date to find your life path number. If you end up with 2, this guide covers your core personality. Use the free life path number calculator below to check, or read the <a href="/learn/how-to-calculate-life-path-number/" class="text-violet hover:text-soft-gold underline">full step-by-step guide to calculating your life path number</a>.
 </p>

 <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:1.5rem;">
 <a href="/learn/life-path-number/#calculator" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;background:var(--color-violet);color:white;font-weight:700;font-size:0.95rem;padding:0.875rem 1.75rem;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">
 Calculate your life path number free
 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
 </a>
 </div>
 </section>

 <!-- FAQ -->
 <section id="faq" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
 <h2 class="section-h2">Frequently asked questions</h2>

 <div class="faq-list">
 {[
 {
 q: "What does it mean to have a life path of 2?",
 a: "Having life path number 2 means your core personality is oriented toward cooperation, empathy, and relationship. You're probably a natural mediator - someone who instinctively reads the room, avoids confrontation, and works to create peace and harmony rather than conflict. The meaning of life path number 2 in your numerology chart is that your life purpose involves connection, partnership, and learning to balance your own needs with your instinct to put others first. People with a life path number 2 often find that their most meaningful growth comes through close relationships rather than individual achievement.",
 },
 {
 q: "Why is life path 2 rare?",
 a: "Life path 2 is considered rare because the arithmetic of birth dates makes it statistically less common than some other numbers. To get a 2, your full birth date needs to reduce to exactly 2 - and given the distribution of calendar dates, certain life path numbers come up more frequently than others. Life path 11 also doesn't reduce to a 2 (it stays as 11), which removes some dates from the pool. The traits themselves - deep empathy, patience, and a genuine preference for cooperation over competition - do feel less common in everyday life, which reinforces the perception.",
 },
 {
 q: "Who should life path number 2 marry?",
 a: "The best life path matches for a 2 are typically 1, 6, and 9. Life path 1 provides the decisiveness and direction that 2 sometimes lacks, while the 2's emotional depth balances the 1's tendency to focus outward. Life path 6 is another natural match - both value home, harmony, and deep loyalty. Life path 9's broad compassion pairs well with the 2's personal warmth. Two life path 2s together can work beautifully, but both partners' tendency to avoid confrontation can mean important things go unsaid. Life path 5 is typically the most challenging match for the 2: the 5 needs freedom and movement, while the 2 needs closeness and consistency.",
 },
 {
 q: "Does life path number 2 attract money?",
 a: "Not directly. Of all the life paths, the 2 is not the most financially driven. That's more the territory of life path 8. But life path 2 individuals often do well professionally over time because people trust them, want to work with them, and advocate for them. They build strong networks through genuine care rather than strategy. In careers in counseling, mediation, healthcare, and people-oriented fields, they often rise steadily. The financial story for a 2 is usually tied to doing work that aligns with their life purpose - when that alignment is there, the resources tend to follow.",
 },
 {
 q: "What is the spiritual meaning of life path 2?",
 a: "The spiritual meaning of life path 2 is about learning to balance giving and receiving. The 2 comes into this life with a strong capacity for love, compassion, and connection - their role as a bridge between people is genuine. The spiritual path for the 2 involves developing a stronger relationship with the self: learning that their own needs matter as much as anyone else's, that saying no isn't selfish, and that authentic self-expression is part of the work, not a distraction from it. Practices like meditation and yoga tend to resonate strongly with this number.",
 },
 {
 q: "What is life path 11's connection to life path 2?",
 a: "Life path 11 is a master number that, when reduced, becomes a 2. People with life path 11 share many of the 2's qualities : sensitivity, intuition, and a strong relational intelligence : but carry them at a higher level of intensity. Where the 2 supports, the 11 inspires. Not everyone with an 11 in their birth date qualifies as a master number - it depends on how the full date reduces. Those who do tend to experience the 2's challenges (emotional overwhelm, self-doubt, people-pleasing) in amplified form.",
 },
 ].map(item => (
